# Nixthon

This package enables calls nix-shell _via_ python. It works on Unix system and Windows (by using wsl and the Nixos Image).

# Installation

## On Unix systems
Install nix.

## On Windows
Install WSL and a NixOS image. See [here](https://nixos.wiki/wiki/WSL).

